OL,4,CDairy giant Arla says driver crisis
OL,5,Chitting milk supply
OL,6, Dairy giant Arla, which supplies milk
OL,7, to all major UK supermarkets, has said
OL,8, a lorry driver shortage has forced it
OL,9, to cut back on its deliveries.
OL,11,FUK managing director, Ash Amirahmadi,
OL,12,Fsaid the firm normally supplied 2,400
OL,13,Fstores a day, but had been experiencing
OL,14,Fdriver shortages since early April.
OL,16,F"Last Saturday, there were 600 stores
OL,17,Fthat we couldn't deliver milk to," he
OL,18,Ftold the BBC.
OL,20,FAnd he warned of a summer of disruption
OL,21,Fand urged the government to act.
